high_descs: Turn left to face the basketball on the floor.
Pick up the basketball on the floor.
Walk around to face the side of the white table.
Place the basketball in the center of the white table.
anns.task_desc: To pick up a basketball and place it on the white table.

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the white table.
Pick up the basketball from under the table.
Carry the basketball and turn left, then right to face the table on the right.
Place the basketball on the table, in the center.
anns.task_desc: Move a basketball from the floor to the table.

high_descs: Make a right to face the white desk.
Pick up a basketball from underneath the desk.
Walk around the desk to face the front of it.
Set the basketball down on top of the white desk.
anns.task_desc: Move a basketball from underneath the white desk to on top of it.
